org.mozilla.geckoview

Interface GeckoSession.PromptDelegate

  • Enclosing class:
    GeckoSession

    public static interface GeckoSession.PromptDelegate
    GeckoSession applications implement this interface to handle prompts triggered by content in the GeckoSession, such as alerts, authentication dialogs, and select list pickers.

      • onButtonPrompt

        @UiThread
void onButtonPrompt(@NonNull
                              GeckoSession session,
                              @Nullable
                              String title,
                              @Nullable
                              String msg,
                              @Nullable
                              String[] btnMsg,
                              @NonNull
                              GeckoSession.PromptDelegate.ButtonCallback callback)
        Display a prompt with up to three buttons.
        Parameters:
        session - GeckoSession that triggered the prompt
        title - Title for the prompt dialog.
        msg - Message for the prompt dialog.
        btnMsg - Array of 3 elements indicating labels for the individual buttons. btnMsg[BUTTON_TYPE_POSITIVE] is the label for the "positive" button. btnMsg[BUTTON_TYPE_NEUTRAL] is the label for the "neutral" button. btnMsg[BUTTON_TYPE_NEGATIVE] is the label for the "negative" button. The button is hidden if the corresponding label is null.
        callback - Callback interface.

      • onChoicePrompt

        @UiThread
void onChoicePrompt(@NonNull
                              GeckoSession session,
                              @Nullable
                              String title,
                              @Nullable
                              String msg,
                              int type,
                              @NonNull
                              GeckoSession.PromptDelegate.Choice[] choices,
                              @NonNull
                              GeckoSession.PromptDelegate.ChoiceCallback callback)
        Display a menu prompt or list prompt.
        Parameters:
        session - GeckoSession that triggered the prompt
        title - Title for the prompt dialog, or null for no title.
        msg - Message for the prompt dialog, or null for no message.
        type - One of CHOICE_TYPE_* indicating the type of prompt.
        choices - Array of Choices each representing an item or group.
        callback - Callback interface.

        Display a color prompt.

        session - GeckoSession that triggered the prompt
        title - Title for the prompt dialog.
        value - Initial color value in HTML color format.
        callback - Callback interface; the result passed to confirm() must be in HTML color format.

      • onDateTimePrompt

        @UiThread
void onDateTimePrompt(@NonNull
                                GeckoSession session,
                                @Nullable
                                String title,
                                int type,
                                @Nullable
                                String value,
                                @Nullable
                                String min,
                                @Nullable
                                String max,
                                @NonNull
                                GeckoSession.PromptDelegate.TextCallback callback)
        Display a date/time prompt.
        Parameters:
        session - GeckoSession that triggered the prompt
        title - Title for the prompt dialog; currently always null.
        type - One of DATETIME_TYPE_* indicating the type of prompt.
        value - Initial date/time value in HTML date/time format.
        min - Minimum date/time value in HTML date/time format.
        max - Maximum date/time value in HTML date/time format.
        callback - Callback interface; the result passed to confirm() must be in HTML date/time format.

      • onFilePrompt

        @UiThread
void onFilePrompt(@NonNull
                            GeckoSession session,
                            @Nullable
                            String title,
                            int type,
                            @Nullable
                            String[] mimeTypes,
                            @NonNull
                            GeckoSession.PromptDelegate.FileCallback callback)
        Display a file prompt.
        Parameters:
        session - GeckoSession that triggered the prompt
        title - Title for the prompt dialog.
        type - One of FILE_TYPE_* indicating the prompt type.
        mimeTypes - Array of permissible MIME types for the selected files, in the form "type/subtype", where "type" and/or "subtype" can be "*" to indicate any value.
        callback - Callback interface.

      • onPopupRequest

        @UiThread
GeckoResult<AllowOrDeny> onPopupRequest(@NonNull
                                                  GeckoSession session,
                                                  @Nullable
                                                  String targetUri)
        Display a popup request prompt; this occurs when content attempts to open a new window in a way that doesn't appear to be the result of user input.
        Parameters:
        session - GeckoSession that triggered the prompt
        targetUri - The target URI for the popup
        Returns:
        A GeckoResult resolving to a AllowOrDeny which indicates whether or not the popup should be allowed to open.
